summary: ABDL reskin of default underwear (Female only.)
descriptionHtml:
ABDL (diaper) reskin of nude females. Definitely not lore-friendly. Probably.

This mod edits femaleunderwear.dds and femaleunderwear_n.dds
Definitely not compatable with other underwear mods and/or nudity mods (It's a reskin of the default female underwear).

If you want to make a request, leave a comment. I saved all the source files so I can make adjustments.

Sorry the screenshots suck! If you want to upload a new image for me, that'd be awesome.
author: pmjosh
